caption:
pairing: eve/villanelle

song: beyoncé - haunted

i shifted the pitch a tiny bit and youtube let me upload it! anyway what i forgot to mention in the vimeo post is that this focuses on some recurring motifs in the show like hands and destruction that come together to highlight the erotic side of obsession between eve and villanelle imo. also i wanted to emphasise the smaller parallels between them that i’ve picked up on having rewatched like a million times at this point. watch in HD!!
